            <h2>Vision</h2>
            <p class="lead">To provide a modern, enterprise-ready Content Management System that combines the best practices of SharePoint with the flexibility and performance of .NET 10 and Blazor.</p>
            
            <h2>Architecture Philosophy</h2>
            <p>OrkinosaiCMS is built on Clean Architecture principles, ensuring:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Maintainability</strong>: Clear separation of concerns makes the codebase easy to understand and modify</li>
                <li><strong>Testability</strong>: Dependency injection and interface-based design enable comprehensive testing</li>
                <li><strong>Extensibility</strong>: Plugin architecture allows unlimited customization without modifying core code</li>
                <li><strong>Scalability</strong>: Cloud-ready architecture designed for Azure and other platforms</li>
            </ul>
            
